Package: BTYDplus
Type: Package
Title: Extension of R Package BTYD
Version: 0.6.4
Date: 2016-02-23
Author: Michael Platzer <michael.platzer@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Michael Platzer <michael.platzer@gmail.com>
Description: Extends the functionality of BTYD package by providing methods for
    parameter estimation and scoring for NBD, G/G/NBD, MBG/NBD, BG/CNBD-k and
    MBG/CNBD-k models, as well as MCMC samples for Pareto/NBD,
    Abe's Pareto/NBD variant and Pareto/GGG.
License: GPL-3
LinkingTo: Rcpp
Imports:
    Rcpp (>= 0.11.1),
    BTYD (>= 2.3),
    coda,
    data.table,
    mvtnorm,
    bayesm,
    gsl
Roxygen: list(wrap = FALSE)
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
